<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/images/K_Logo_2.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Logo">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">2024 MegazoneCloud ISV Conference Day</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            The First Ever ISV Conference<br>
                            일시: 2024년 6월 18일(화) 12:00 - 20:30<br>
                            장소: 그랜드 인터컨티넨탈 서울 파르나스, 그랜드볼룸 5F<br>
                            문의: event@megazone.com<br><br>
                            안녕하세요.<br><br>
                            귀사의 무궁한 발전을 기원하며, 2024 MegazoneCloud ISV Conference Day에
                            초대의 말씀을 드립니다.
                            ISV를 위한 특별한 행사로 ISV가 가진 가능성을 최대로 발휘하도록 하기 위해
                            MegazoneCloud는 AWS, Intel과 함께 합니다.
                            이번 행사는 다양한 세션, 데모, 네트워킹을 통해
                            귀사의 비즈니스를 확장하는 데 도움이 될 것입니다.
                            많은 관심과 참석 부탁드립니다.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">행사 상세 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="text-center">사전 등록하기</h2>
                <form action="/register" method="post">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">이름</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="company">회사</label>
                        <input type="text" id="company" name="company" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="department">부서</label>
                        <input type="text" id="department" name="department" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="position">직급</label>
                        <input type="text" id="position" name="position" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">이메일</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="phone">휴대전화번호</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="attendance">참석 여부</label>
                        <select id="attendance" name="attendance" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="yes">예</option>
                            <option value="no">아니오</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="gift">기념품 선택</label>
                        <select id="gift" name="gift" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="gift1">기념품1</option>
                            <option value="gift2">기념품2</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="agreements">동의 사항</label>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="agreement1" name="agreement1" class="form-check-input">
                            <label for="agreement1" class="form-check-label">개인정보 수집/이용 동의</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="agreement2" name="agreement2" class="form-check-input">
                            <label for="agreement2" class="form-check-label">개인정보 제3자 제공 동의</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">사전 등록하기</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-4">
        <p class="mb-0">Copyright © 2024 MegazoneCloud Corp. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
